      <h1 class='title'>Tax Collection (Costs)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1658WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1658ws' title='Col. 1658WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1658WS' name='column_1658ws' href='#column_1658ws' rel='bookmark'>1658WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_47'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tim-loughton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_47' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tim Loughton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tim-loughton" title="Mr Tim Loughton">Tim Loughton</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Chancellor of the Exchequer what the cost of collection of<span class="italic">(a)</span> national insurance,<span class="italic">(b)</span> income tax,<span class="italic">(c)</span> capital gains tax and<span class="italic">(d)</span> inheritance tax was in each year since 1997. [189430]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_48'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-dawn-primarolo' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_48' title='Link to this speech by Ms Dawn Primarolo' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-dawn-primarolo" title="Ms Dawn Primarolo">Dawn Primarolo</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">For years up to and including 2001&#x2013;02, the costs of collecting income tax, capital gains tax, inheritance tax and national insurance contributions can be found on page 45 of the Inland Revenue Annual Report for the year ending 31 March 2002 (published in December 2002). Figures for 2002&#x2013;03 are contained within Appendix 2 of the Inland Revenue Annual Report for the year ending 31 March 2003 (published in December 2003).</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
